Convert MySQL databases to RSS feeds. <a href="http://www.feedforall.com/sql2rss.htm" target="_blank" >SQL2RSS</a> , a new PHP script, dynamically generates RSS feeds based on a database query. <br />
<br />
The <a href="http://www.feedforall.com/sql2rss.htm" target="_blank" >SQL2RSS</a> Script joins the RSS Scripts Directory. Access to the <a href="http://www.feedforall.com/scripts-directory.htm" target="_blank" >RSS scripts directory</a> is free to all registered users of FeedForAll and FeedForAll Mac, or access can be purchased for $ 29.95.&nbsp;&nbsp;
